'''= Dutch-Language blog dedicated to bringing the renewable revolution to the forefront of public discussion'''

URL:http://www.zeronaut.be/

=== Description===
Zeronaut.be is a dutch-language blog in collaboration with mo.be dedicated to sharing stories and opinion pieces about renewable energy, the sharing economy, and other elements of sustainable and social innovation. Their mission is to provide an open-platform alternative to the traditional media and keep the debate on renewable innovation balanced, rather than heavily influenced by special interests.  According to their website: "Zeronaut.be made it her job to talk about anything that was not business as usual". Due to its open-platform structure, anyone can share news, views and opinions on the sustainable revolution. The receive and share countless blogposts from experts who share their views and knowledge, which made Zeronaut a database of inspiring examples, but also a network of critical voices and committed doers.

